00:01:25.818 --> 00:01:29.688 line:0%
We work as a team.
We're together 24/ 7,

00:01:29.688 --> 00:01:30.423
which is--

00:01:30.523 --> 00:01:31.691
We are married, you know.

00:01:31.691 --> 00:01:32.992
Yes, we are married.

00:01:32.992 --> 00:01:35.495
But it's a good partnership.

